#CHIP SegaPCM
#CLOCK 7670454

; SegaPCM Pitch Sweep Test
;
; Tests pitch modulation capabilities:
; - Frequency sweep up
; - Frequency sweep down
; - Rapid frequency changes
; - Register write accuracy for pitch control

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Pitch sweep up: C4 to C5
c4 . . d4 . . e4 . . f4 . . g4 . . a4 . . b4 . . >c5 .

r4

; Pitch sweep down: C5 to C4
>c5 . . b4 . . a4 . . g4 . . f4 . . e4 . . d4 . . c4 .

r4

r2

#END
